120.
</S>
<S ID="80865">
J'ai l'intention d'exposer en détail la conception du développement retenue par l'ONU dans le Programme d'action pour le développement et un rapport préliminaire sur la question sera soumis à l'Assemblée générale lors de sa quarante-huitième session.
