</S>
<S ID="221183">
Conformément au paragraphe 1 de la résolution 834 (1993) du Conseil de sécurité, j'ai réduit les effectifs de la Mission qui ne compte plus que 43 civils recrutés sur le plan international, 50 observateurs militaires, 18 observateurs de la police et une équipe paramédicale composée de 11 militaires, ainsi que le personnel local nécessaire.
