</S>
<S ID="221956">
321.
</S>
<S ID="222150">
En octobre 1992, j'ai dépêché une mission en Arménie et en Azerbaïdjan pour qu'elle y enquête sur la situation provoquée par le conflit du Haut-Karabakh, l'enclave arménienne en Azerbaïdjan.
